Subject: drm/amdgpu: Add a new flag for SR-IOV to share memory between PF & VF
Git-commit: 20a3a71da542974a7ba30b121c5f81b83579c828
Patch-mainline: v4.15-rc1
References: FATE#326289 FATE#326079 FATE#326049 FATE#322398 FATE#326166

Add ATOM_VRAM_BLOCK_SRIOV_MSG_SHARE_RESERVATION to identify whether
driver need to reserve VRAM for SR-IOV shared memory.

